metadata.description:
Sam Larsen. 

Paranoid, keeps to himself mostly. Has his body augmented with military-grade cyber augments from his time in the privately-funded military. 

Ever since he blew the whistle on the atrocities committed in the Great War, he couldn't quite shake off the feeling that something or someone is watching him. Takes odd jobs as a merc.
